CBRE are pleased to offer for lease this 'A' Grade warehousing at competitive rates.

This is a modern well designed warehouse with excellent truck access, canopies over doorway and substantial hardstand if required.

This building can be leased in separate areas from 2,375sqm* to 6,950sqm*. Attached is a plan of the building.

Additional hardstand can be made available if required.

Area 1: 2,375sqm*
Area 2: 2,370sqm*
Area 3: 2,201sqm* (over head cranes)

Rental rates are available upon request.

DESCRIPTION
The property comprises a quality two-level office, workshop, hangar and airside apron. The office contains a mix of partitioned offices, meeting/training rooms and staff amenities to both levels.

Located in the tightly held Jandakot Airport precinct. The property can be used for a variety of uses subject to approval from the Jandakot Airport Holdings Pty Ltd.


KEY FEATURES
+ Dedicated airside apron
+ 12m* sliding door opening
+ Front roller door access point
+ Exceptional staff amenities

Excellent opportunity to co-locate within a pre-existing successful business active in the tourism industry. Facility features excellent quality office/amenities, immaculate hangar with apron and excellent car parking.

Ideal for aviation based business or non-aviation business looking for office and storage space in an excellent location with easy access to freeways and Roe Highway
 
- Office $135/sqm pa + GST and variable outgoings
- Hangar $55/sqm pa + GST and variable outgoings
- Portion of apron and car parking included
 
Flexible allocation based on between 30% and 50% of the total facility which incorporates a total office area of 108sqm* and a total hangar area of 589sqm*.
